'''2016年慕尼黑槍擊案'''為發生在2016年7月22日（UTC+2），位於[[德国|德国]][[慕尼黑|慕尼黑]][[莫萨赫|莫萨赫]]境內的{{le|奧林匹亞購物中心|Olympia-Einkaufszentrum (shopping mall)}}附近之一宗槍擊事件<ref name="bbc">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-36870874|title=Munich shooting: Police say nine dead as manhunt continues|website=BBC News|date=2016-07-22|access-date=22 July 2016|archive-date=2017-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224080239/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-36870874|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="independent">{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/munich-shooting-shots-fired-oez-shopping-centre-mall-germany-city-munchen-armed-police-a7151186.html|title=Munich shooting: 'Shots fired' at OEZ shopping centre in German city|work=The Independent|date=2016-07-22|language=en-GB|access-date=22 July 2016|first=Siobhan|last=Fenton|archive-date=2016-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723171326/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/munich-shooting-shots-fired-oez-shopping-centre-mall-germany-city-munchen-armed-police-a7151186.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方發言人表示此宗槍擊事件造成多名民眾死亡和受傷<ref name="guardian">{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/jul/22/munich-shooting-police-evacuate-shopping-centre-live |title=Munich shooting: police say several people killed in 'rampage' – live |work=The Guardian |date=2016-07-22 |accessdate=2016-07-22 |first=Kevin |last=Rawlinson |archive-date=2016-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160722174331/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/jul/22/munich-shooting-police-evacuate-shopping-centre-live |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此宗槍擊事件從購物中心附近的[[麦当劳|麦当劳]]開始。官方表示嫌犯為帶有德國與伊朗血統的獨行槍手，而槍手犯案後即舉槍自盡<ref name=BBCLive/><ref name="welt">{{cite web|url=http://www.welt.de/politik/deutschland/article157237504/Mehrere-Tote-bei-Schuessen-an-Muenchner-Einkaufszentrum.html|title=Tote bei Schüssen an Einkaufszentrum – offenbar Schüsse am Stachus|trans-title=Deaths in shooting at mall – apparently shots at Stachus|date=2016-07-22|publisher=Die Welt|accessdate=2016-07-22|via=Welt Online|language=de|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912101214/https://www.welt.de/politik/deutschland/article157237504/Muenchener-treffen-sich-zum-spontanen-Gedenken-am-Tatort.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Welt2>{{cite news|url=http://www.welt.de/politik/deutschland/article157237504/Taeter-hat-sich-vermutlich-selbst-getoetet-und-alleine-gehandelt.html|title=Täter hat sich vermutlich selbst getötet und alleine gehandelt|trans-title=Offender has probably killed himself and acted alone|last=Barfuss|first=Thore|date=2016-07-22|last2=Tann|first2=Marie von der|newspaper=Welt Online|access-date=22 July 2016|language=de|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912101214/https://www.welt.de/politik/deutschland/article157237504/Muenchener-treffen-sich-zum-spontanen-Gedenken-am-Tatort.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="welt10">{{cite web|url=http://www.welt.de/politik/deutschland/article157237504/Mutmasslicher-Taeter-ist-18-jaehriger-Deutsch-Iraner-aus-Muenchen.html|title=Täter soll 18-jähriger Deutsch-Iraner sein|trans-title=Shooter is probably of German-Iranian descent|date=2016-07-22|publisher=Die Welt|accessdate=2016-07-22|via=Welt Online|language=de|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912101215/https://www.welt.de/politik/deutschland/article157237504/Muenchener-treffen-sich-zum-spontanen-Gedenken-am-Tatort.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

兇徒是18歲的戴维·阿里·桑波里，沒有持槍執照，犯案武器是一把[[格洛克17|格洛克17]]式[[半自動手槍|半自動手槍]]，懷疑是通過互聯網非法購得<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://paper.wenweipo.com/2016/07/25/GJ1607250028.htm |title=「暗網」非法買槍 揭德槍管漏洞 |publisher=香港文匯報 |date=2016-07-25 |accessdate=2016-07-25 |archive-date=2016-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161004002559/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2016/07/25/GJ1607250028.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。警方事後在他的背包裡發現還有約300發子彈。<ref name=people01>{{Cite news |url=http://world.people.com.cn/n1/2016/0724/c1002-28579568.html |title=慕尼黑枪击案10人身亡 中国游客均报平安 |publisher=人民網 |date=2016-07-24 |accessdate=2016-07-24 |archive-date=2016-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160724163007/http://world.people.com.cn/n1/2016/0724/c1002-28579568.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

6男3女在本次槍擊案中遇害，其中7人未滿20歲，最年輕的2名死者只有13歲。死者包括2名[[科索沃|科索沃]]人、3名[[土耳其|土耳其]]人、1名德國出生的[[希臘|希臘]]公民，另一名死者有科索沃血統。<ref name=Guardian.Victims>{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/23/victims-of-munich-shooting-were-predominately-teenagers |title=Who were the Munich shooting victims? Eight of nine dead under 20 years old |work=The Guardian |date=2016-07-24 |first=Chris |last=Johnston |accessdate=2016-07-25 |archive-date=2016-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160724204427/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/23/victims-of-munich-shooting-were-predominately-teenagers |dead-url=no }}</ref>警方認為大部分死者有移民背景只是巧合，因為案發地點的麥當勞有許多移民子女經常光顧。<ref>{{cite news|title=Ali S. hatte eigenes Manifest verfasst|trans-title=Ali S. had written own manifesto|url=http://www.zeit.de/gesellschaft/zeitgeschehen/2016-07/amoklaeufer-muenchen-waffe-darknet|work=Die Zeit|date=24 July 2016|accessdate=24 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160724171341/http://www.zeit.de/gesellschaft/zeitgeschehen/2016-07/amoklaeufer-muenchen-waffe-darknet|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過後來有報道稱所有9名遇害者都有移民背景，而伊朗裔兇徒桑波里以「[[雅利安人|雅利安人]]」自居，並仇視阿拉伯人和土耳其人，警方正在調查他是否刻意挑選外國人殺害。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%85%95%E5%B0%BC%E9%BB%91%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB%E6%A1%88%E5%87%B6%E6%89%8B%E7%96%91%E6%9C%89%E6%9E%81%E5%8F%B3%E7%BF%BC%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF/a-19430956 |title=慕尼黑枪击案凶手疑有极右翼背景 |publisher=德國之聲 |date=2016-07-27 |accessdate=2016-08-18 |archive-date=2016-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728170548/http://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%85%95%E5%B0%BC%E9%BB%91%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB%E6%A1%88%E5%87%B6%E6%89%8B%E7%96%91%E6%9C%89%E6%9E%81%E5%8F%B3%E7%BF%BC%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF/a-19430956 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

德国警方已逮捕桑波里的1名16岁阿富汗友人，认为其知情不報，並有可能涉及事前在[[臉書|臉書]]貼文引誘其他人來到槍擊案發生地點。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://cn.rfi.fr/contenu/20160725-%E6%85%95%E5%B0%BC%E9%BB%91%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB-%E5%BE%B7%E8%AD%A6%E9%80%AE%E5%87%B6%E6%89%8B16%E5%B2%81%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA |title=慕尼黑枪击 德警逮凶手16岁阿富汗友人 |publisher=法廣 |date=2016-07-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160725133504/http://cn.rfi.fr/contenu/20160725-%E6%85%95%E5%B0%BC%E9%BB%91%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB-%E5%BE%B7%E8%AD%A6%E9%80%AE%E5%87%B6%E6%89%8B16%E5%B2%81%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E5%8F%8B%E4%BA%BA |archivedate=2016-07-25 |accessdate=2016-07-25 }}</ref>

2016年8月17日，德國警方宣佈於8月16日拘捕一名被懷疑向桑波里出售犯案槍械的31歲男子。據報桑波里以4000多歐元購買槍支和子彈。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E5%BA%93%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E6%85%95%E5%B0%BC%E9%BB%91%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB%E6%A1%88%E5%8D%96%E6%9E%AA%E8%80%85%E8%90%BD%E7%BD%91/a-19481948 |title=武器库曝光！慕尼黑枪击案"卖枪者"落网 |publisher=德國之聲 |date=2016-08-18 |accessdate=2016-08-18 |archive-date=2016-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819062104/http://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E5%BA%93%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E6%85%95%E5%B0%BC%E9%BB%91%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB%E6%A1%88%E5%8D%96%E6%9E%AA%E8%80%85%E8%90%BD%E7%BD%91/a-19481948 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==調查==
慕尼黑警方於7月23日表示，在槍手桑波里的居所未有找到與伊斯蘭極端主義或「[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]」有關的物品，而桑波里以前曾經因為精神[[抑郁_(情绪)|抑鬱]]而接受治療，本次槍擊案沒有極端伊斯蘭或政治背景。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%85%95%E5%B0%BC%E9%BB%91%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB%E6%A1%88%E5%87%B6%E6%89%8B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E4%BD%9C%E6%A1%88%E5%8A%A8%E6%9C%BA/a-19422822 |title=慕尼黑枪击案："凶手没有政治作案动机" |publisher=德國之聲 |date=2016-07-23 |accessdate=2016-07-23 |archive-date=2016-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160724160444/http://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%85%95%E5%B0%BC%E9%BB%91%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB%E6%A1%88%E5%87%B6%E6%89%8B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E4%BD%9C%E6%A1%88%E5%8A%A8%E6%9C%BA/a-19422822 |dead-url=no }}</ref>警方表示桑波里對於大規模槍擊案有「特殊興趣」，並在其家中搜到一本關於[[校園槍擊案|校園槍擊案]]的書籍《Why Kids Kill: Inside the Minds of School Shooters》。<ref name="independent1">{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/munich-shooting-shopping-centre-mcdonalds-gunman-identified-ali-david-sonboly-german-iranian-suicide-a7152116.html|title=Munich shooting: Ali David Sonboly identified as gunman behind shopping centre attack|date=2016-07-23|work=The Independent|accessdate=2016-07-23|first=Samuel|last=Osborne|archive-date=2016-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723120518/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/munich-shooting-shopping-centre-mcdonalds-gunman-identified-ali-david-sonboly-german-iranian-suicide-a7152116.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>警方表示桑波里可能是[[2011年挪威爆炸和枪击事件|2011年挪威爆炸和枪击事件]]兇徒[[安德斯·贝林·布雷维克|安德斯·贝林·布雷维克]]的崇拜者，很有可能受到該案影響而犯案，而行兇的日子正就是挪威槍擊案發生5周年之日。<ref name=people01/><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.cri.cn/2016-07-24/e0bbd5f2-5faa-4342-4876-29902c389eb2.html |title=德慕尼黑枪手与IS无关 或曾“邀请”受害者赴事发地 |work=国际在线 |date=2016-07-24 |accessdate=2016-07-25 |archive-date=2016-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918143939/http://news.cri.cn/2016-07-24/e0bbd5f2-5faa-4342-4876-29902c389eb2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

